(636, 4, '2018-10-22 08:54:40', '2018-10-22 08:54:40', '<strong><img class=\"wp-image-629 aligncenter\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" /></strong>\r\n\r\nCredit: Wedding Creation BD\r\n\r\n<strong>We know when it comes to jewelry, brides love to garb themselves with something unique, new and trendy. And THAT is where floral jewelry steps in as the trendiest form of ornaments. More than often you will see brides opting to use natural flowers in the form of necklaces, earpieces, kalires, and flower crowns so much so that they use minimal metallic ornaments to give more focus to these flowers. And we can’t blame the brides for doing so as floral jewelry look so beautiful, vibrant and colorful compared to the monotonous traditional jewelry.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-626 size-medium\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-7-226x300.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"226\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nCredit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/95\">Rifat Reza Photography &amp; Cinematography</a>\r\n\r\nWith the boom of this trend, flowers are now not only used for venue decoration but are also used to enhance the beauty of the brides as well.\r\nFloral jewelry comes in a wide variety of sizes and styles. The best thing about them is that you can combine your jewelry in any type of colors to match your outfit or venue theme.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4><strong>FLORAL JEWELRY STYLES</strong></h4>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-621 size-medium\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-2-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nCredit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/89\">Reminiscence Photography</a>\r\n\r\nThe usual floral jewelry set includes earrings, necklace, tikli, bracelet, anklets, and kalire. Depending upon your choice of clothing and the color, complement the type of flower you would make your ornaments with. Usually, it is easier to make ornaments out of smaller flowers rather than the larger ones. Flowers such as- roses, orchids, rajanigandha, and jasmine flowers are the most popular types of flowers to make this type of jewelry. However, if using natural flowers is not your preference, you can still go for floral designs made out of plastic, silk or any other fabric you prefer.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-630 size-medium\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-10-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nCredit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/109\">জলছাপ</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4><strong>LONGEVITY OF THE JEWELRY</strong></h4>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-622 size-medium\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-3-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nCredit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/88\">Wedding Moments</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>You might raise questions about the longevity of floral jewelry. So it is our utmost duty to let you know that you can breathe a sigh of relief. Because floral pieces of jewelry last a whole day and even up to 3-4 days if refrigerated. If you’re placing your order to a designer or in any local shop, make sure to place the order at least 15-20 days before. You will need to be in touch with your designer every now and then. Making sure that your design has been nailed right down to your preference is a must. Since these type of jewelry are free size, brides don’t need to appoint schedules for measurement trials.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-620 size-medium\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-1-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nCredit: L\'FOTTO\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4><strong>INEXPENSIVE AND EASY</strong></h4>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-627 size-medium\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-8-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nCredit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/90\">Wedding Divine</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Using flowers as a form of jewelry has many advantages. They are a lot cheaper in making, but they do not look cheap in any way. They are easier to make and purchase. Floral ornaments are lighter than metallic ornaments exempting the brides from feeling heavy from all the clothing and jewelry.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-623\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-4-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\n\r\nCredit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/87\">Wedding Diary</a>\r\n<h4><strong>THE CROWN AND KALIRE</strong></h4>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-625 size-medium\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-6-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n\r\nsource: Pinterest\r\n\r\n<strong>One thing we have spotted on the floral jewelry trend is the widespread use of flower crown and floral kalire. Floral crowns are very simple but yet it beautifies the bride on any occasion. Using orchid or white/red rose to make floral crowns is usually the best choice. The color contrast looks good in e</strong><strong>very theme and orchid and roses usually last longer.</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-624 size-medium\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/NEW-AND-TRENDING-BRIDAL-FLORAL-JEWELRY-5-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY \" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>In the ca</strong><strong>se of ka</strong><strong>lires, use lighter and smaller flowers to make, as heavier flowers are more prone to tangling and quite often gets in the way of simple tasks. Don’t restrict yourself from moving around by wearing your floral kalire in only one hand.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>So, take a time out from the traditional gold-diamond-silver jewelry, and take a chance with floral jewelry. We promise you that you won’t be disappointed. Because we want our brides to be a trendsetter at their very own wedding.</strong>', 'NEW AND TRENDING BRIDAL FLORAL JEWELRY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '569-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-22 08:54:40', '2018-10-22 08:54:40', '', 569, 'https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/2018/10/22/569-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
