(801, 4, '2018-11-05 09:19:33', '2018-11-05 09:19:33', 'Whether you’re tying the knot with your long-term college or university sweetheart, or you found the perfect soul mate through mutual friends or family members, we believe that every single modern love story is unique and different. That story is reflected upon each modern wedding that has its own set of uniqueness. With each passing year, the art of wedding events, cultures, fashion and even dance routines for your Holud has changed. So why Photography should be left behind? Photographs are the best way to tell YOUR unique story for YOUR wedding. Below are some ideas and themes that you can implement in your wedding to make your dream event more vibrant, colorful and AWESOME!\r\n<h5><strong>BLACK &amp; WHITE PHOTOGRAPHS</strong></h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-738\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/37372176_2186646301377303_1930338768758243328_o-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" />Credit: Wedding Diary</p>\r\nWe know, garbing your entire wedding photo album with black and white photographs is a big ask. Still, we cannot help but admire how beautiful and gorgeous the bride and groom look in black &amp; white. While some might argue that it makes the pictures look bland, grim and monotonous, but we believe it makes the photographs more elegant. There’s something about this colorless filter that drains out all the other vibrancy. Instead, it puts more focus on the emotions of the subjects in the pictures!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-735\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/36771293_2164692453572688_1466317833607577600_o-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-726\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/31491537_1090873837732192_3238380804035837952_n-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"639\" height=\"960\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-700\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/17436261_1380983231967473_1520416407027438707_o-1024x684.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-692\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/12190788_454646128055521_4576660466859453072_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-689\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/10896960_836407363113056_5031240811069031143_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-771\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/image016.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-758\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/image002.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"689\" height=\"487\" />\r\n<h5><strong>THE SQUAD PHOTOS</strong></h5>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-728\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/31958157_1797762953623319_6414312306846466048_o-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" />\r\n\r\nInstead of those clichéd portrait photographs, get your friends and cousins in for some music-album-cover-esque photo-shoot. Since everyone will be decked up in their best dresses, the pictures are bound to look cool and fun. Strike out different poses or any foolish ones too! The sillier the picture, the cooler.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-707\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/22181537_1670669392946057_8029686032657759833_o-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-702\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/19054944_1411816232238830_6488853774274687734_o-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" />\r\n<h5><strong>FLOWER CROWNS<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-785\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/image030-1024x684.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" /></strong></h5>\r\nA new look for modern brides to express their personal style while garbing themselves with the traditional clothing. Instead of donning yourself with the veil of your saree or lehenga, you and your friends and relatives can wear flower crowns. Colors combinations can be totally changed depending on the types of flowers you will use. Moreover, this will create a whole new theme for your event with an extra touch of personalization. The bravura of the crown can vary from rustic to fanciful and the photographs are bound to look beautiful.<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-749\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42592049_2322784101096855_3753810981596168192_o-1024x726.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"454\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-790\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/image035.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"416\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-699\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/17388951_1302670893120885_131529104281520427_o-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" />\r\n<h5><strong>THE HOLI COLORS</strong></h5>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-731\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/36269155_1849400335098629_1712949389913227264_o-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" />Whether you use holi colors for pre-wedding or post-wedding, the pictures that will come out will look absolutely stunning and fun.  You get to have fun throwing all these colors at your friends and cousins while having all those intimate moments captured in colors. Find an outdoor place, or book a resort if you have to. Wear all white for better color contrast photographs.<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-799\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/image017-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"960\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-800\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/aa-1024x665.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"416\" />', '4 unique and trending theme of Photographs for your wedding!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '526-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-05 09:19:33', '2018-11-05 09:19:33', '', 526, 'https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/2018/11/05/526-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
