(550, 4, '2018-11-08 09:44:37', '2018-11-08 09:44:37', '<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/36410191_1861309160602031_1776284081466638336_n.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/88\">Wedding Moments</a></p>\r\nYour skincare represents a huge part of your wedding look. Obviously, cosmetics and makeup form an important part too, but like everything else, a decent base is the most essential factor in getting an incredible look on your wedding day! Moreover, a good skin is imperative when you’re on your wedding day among hundreds of people and you won\'t have any sort of makeup to put on before getting that exclusive wedding picture.\r\n\r\nSo we have come up with some tips on bridal skincare that you should follow through before your big day!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-649\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/BRIDAL-SKINCARE-2.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/86\">Retro Focus Photography</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4><strong>Eating right and sleeping on time</strong></h4>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-656\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lionesse-eat-healthy-for-great-skin-hair-and-nails.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-653\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/gin-and-juice-3-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nIt doesn’t matter how much worth of makeup you put on your face, if you don’t eat and sleep right, your make up won’t stand out and do justice for the amount of time and money you would have invested in your cosmetics. For Brides, this might be a tricky routine to follow. The most important practice is to have a good breakfast stacked with organic juices, fruits, and coconut water. Couple that with a minimum of at least 7 hours of uninterrupted sleep truly makes a huge difference on your skin.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642 size-large\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/16991885_802106859938390_6592654392634475891_o-1024x902.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"640\" height=\"564\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/130\">Metro Weddings</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Exfoliating and Masking</strong></h4>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ScrubBar2_1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nIf you’re not much of a skincare person or you don’t want to take those extra steps of making a routine sleep and diet, you can start exfoliating and masking. It is a simple technique that is guaranteed to work. Exfoliating at least once a week, cleansing your skin every day and applying sunscreen in moderation will work wonders for your skin. We advise you to use all these creams from the same brand for better results. In addition, masking 3-4 times a week is a must. Keep in mind, if possible use homemade products rather than those ready-made store products. For dry skin, mix olive oil and egg yolk to be put on your skin to give it a glow and try to use the charcoal mask at least once a month.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-662\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/22851728_1893834734266288_7433735531536124747_n-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE FOR THE WEDDING\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/94\">Photoholic</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/31491537_1090873837732192_3238380804035837952_n.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"400\" height=\"601\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/89\">Reminiscence Photography</a></p>\r\n[carousel_slide id=\'605\']\r\n<h4><strong>Ayurveda for natural skin care treatment</strong></h4>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-658 size-full\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/8-1.png\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"700\" height=\"438\" />\r\n\r\nSwitching to all natural Ayurveda is your best alternative if you don’t want to use the traditional inorganic cosmetic products. Ayurvedic products usually take time to show results. It is advised to start using them at least 6-8 months before your wedding. For best results, slowly cut down fast food or oily food from your daily routine. Even if you do, eat them in moderation. Use vegetable oil if you have to and eating fruits is a must!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/36532340_1866376746761939_1840891552218480640_n.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/88\">Wedding Moments</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/BRIDAL-SKINCARE.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/109\">জলছাপ</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4><strong>Dry Brushing</strong></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Bella-Nani-Dry-Brushing-1024x855.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"600\" height=\"501\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-651\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Electric-Makeup-Brush-Cleaner-Dryer-Set-Make-Up-Brushes-Washing-Tool-Makeup-Brushes-Cleaner-Dry-In_f18f6857-5629-43ce-94fd-0f6f07410ed2_1024x1024@2x-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\nContrary to scientific beliefs, dry brushing has actually helped a lot of people in getting a softer and smoother skin. Even some dermatologists will suggest you try this out. There are a lot of benefits to dry brushing. First, brushing the skin regularly helps stimulate the normal lymph flow under the skin. It helps the body detoxify itself naturally as lymph vessels run under the skin. Second, using a smaller and softer dry brush helps the skin in clearing oil, dirt, and residue from the pores. And third, dry brushing removes dead skins and cells from the surface of the skin and helps reduce cellulite. Find the right brush and use multiple brushes for different parts of your body.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641 size-large\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/16991743_802107129938363_4561969848663676970_o-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/130\">Metro Weddings</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/BRIDAL-SKINCARE-1.jpg\" alt=\"BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit: <a href=\"https://www.ayojok.com/vendors/photography%20and%20cinematography/108\">MAT Photography</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'BRIDAL SKINCARE BEFORE THE WEDDING', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'bridal-skincare-wedding', '', '', '2019-01-02 12:12:30', '2019-01-02 12:12:30', '', 0, 'https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/?p=550', 0, 'post', '', 0),
