ng too bright or a saree or lehenga that is covered with embroideries or embellishments. Wedding Reception', 'What to wear to a Bangladeshi wedding as a female guest', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '343-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-04 10:37:47', '2018-10-04 10:37:47', '', 343, 'https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/2018/10/04/343-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
