(377, 2, '2018-10-06 18:13:43', '2018-10-06 18:13:43', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">As compared to the groom, there are a gazillion ideas for gifting something special to the bride. There are certain wedding gifts that are favored more for gifting the bride than others. Here is a list of few gift items which is loved by most of the newly married girls. Believe me, these are tried and true!</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>1. Jewellery &amp; Jewellery Box</strong></h3>\r\nIt’s pretty hard to go wrong with the jewellery. (Just make sure it’s the right one). This day is a special date to celebrate in the best way possible. Necklaces, earrings, bangles, rings and anklets made of gold and silver, studded with precious semi-precious stones remain the top choice to be gifted to the bride. The bride deserves a gift as special as she is – and what better way to show her your love than with beautiful jewellery she’ll be able to wear and treasure the rest of her life?\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-388\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"385\" />\r\n\r\nJewellery boxes to store all the trinket is also a great idea for gifting.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-379\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-2.jpg\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-378\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-1.png\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"600\" height=\"407\" />\r\n\r\n[carousel_slide id=\'605\']\r\n<h3><strong>2. Makeup and Accessories</strong></h3>\r\nFrom a woman’s perspective, no outfit is complete without the perfect accessory. So, without giving a second thought you can go for.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-391\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"899\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-392\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nA Makeup hamper is perfect gift for a makeup lover. The bride will already be glowing, but this beauty kit filled with polishes and makeup will help her look even more radiant. Philosophy believes that “marriage is a beautiful journey,” which is why they created this gift set for every bride.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-380\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-3-e1538849501994.jpg\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"623\" height=\"576\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-382 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-5.jpg\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"522\" height=\"522\" />\r\n<h3><strong style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', arial, sans-serif; font-size: 22px;\">3. Bags and clutches</strong></h3>\r\nThere is one such gift which is very much liked by most of the women that is Bags and Clutches. Generally, most of the women have at least two-three different types of handbag to fit into the occasion and requirements. Trust me, she’d love it. Just be sure to keep the bride’s trousseau in mind when you shop.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-383 size-full\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-6.jpg\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"591\" height=\"549\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-384\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-7.jpg\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" />\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><strong>4. Kitchen Gadgets</strong></h3>\r\nKitchen Gadget is a perfect gift for a girl looking to set up a new home, it is a great idea to gift some kitchen utensils that are bound to come in handy. Casseroles, non-stick cooking ranges, oven-proof glassware, dinnerware and cutlery sets are the essential items she can’t do without. Gifting these might be a nice way to set her up for their future kitchen.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-387 size-full\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"327\" /><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-386\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"396\" /> <img class=\"size-full wp-image-385 aligncenter\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-8.jpg\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"450\" height=\"288\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFeature Photo by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/zfZmSzr7jHI?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\">rawpixel</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/gift?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\">Unsplash</a>', 'Wedding Gift for Bride', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'wedding-gift-for-bride', '', '', '2019-01-02 12:21:00', '2019-01-02 12:21:00', '', 0, 'https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/?p=377', 0, 'post', '', 0),
