l wp-image-384\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-7.jpg\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />\r\n<h3><strong>4. Kitchen Gadgets</strong></h3>\r\nKitchen Gadget is a perfect gift for a girl looking to set up a new home, it is a great idea to gift some kitchen utensils that are bound to come in handy. Casseroles, non-stick cooking ranges, oven-proof glassware, dinnerware and cutlery sets are the essential items she can’t do without. Gifting these might be a nice way to set her up for their future kitchen.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-386\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"481\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-387\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"327\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-385\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Gifts-for-Bride-8.jpg\" alt=\"Gifts for Bride\" width=\"450\" height=\"288\" />', 'Gifts for Bride', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '377-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-06 17:45:47', '2018-10-06 17:45:47', '', 377, 'https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/2018/10/06/377-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
