(907, 4, '2019-01-09 10:32:13', '2019-01-09 10:32:13', 'We believe your pair of shoe matters as much as your wedding outfit and choosing the right shoes should get as much attention as choosing your outfit. Wedding shoes are the final accessory that will complete and polish your wedding look. While matching the dress with your shoes is absolutely mandatory, comfortability should not be sacrificed too,\r\n\r\nHere are some important factors to consider to buy a pair of shoes:\r\n<h5><strong>Schedule a day to buy shoes</strong>:</h5>\r\n<h5><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-903\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Christian-Louboutin-and-Sabyasachi--1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />If you think choosing the perfect shoe is just a matter of ‘pick and buy’, then you are wrong. You can have a variety of options and choices when it comes to picking your dress, but finding the perfect pair of footwear is not easy, especially shoes that match your outfit and wedding theme. So set aside a day just to browse and buy your footwear. Research beforehand on where the best collections can be found.</h5>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5><strong>Color matters:</strong></h5>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-905\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Punjabi-Jutti3-1024x792.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"495\" />The color of your shoes is a matter of focus while buying. Keep in mind what the color of your outfit is and try to go for a contrasting color match. Do not pick bright colored shoe because that will outdo your outfit making it look odd and not stylish. Moreover, a brighter color footwear will take the attention away from your wedding outfit. For the ladies, pick a color that is very light and variable. This will be a benefit for you like shoes of such colors can be worn with a wide range of dresses for other occasions.\r\n<h5><strong>Picking the perfect design:</strong></h5>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-897\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/12-Bridal-Heels.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"652\" height=\"652\" />There are different types of shoes in the market that you can choose from-<strong> stilettos, peep-toes, wedges, platform heels, loafers, tassel shoes </strong><strong>and more</strong>. Each type of shoe has a specific function and is made to be worn with specific dresses. So choose wisely when going for a specific design type. However, don’t choose anything that is too simplistic because you will want to look elegant for your big day. So pick a fancy design for the fancy occasion.\r\n<h5><strong>Heels or Comfort?</strong></h5>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-895\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/0f637d4d725f50c093a847ae6b03fd6a-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-899\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1786b87af42acde16a68c1030627d949-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />The dilemma that every brides\' face. Choose your heels wisely. If you are someone who is used to wearing heels on a daily basis, you can opt for shoes with high heels. But if you wear heels only during occasions, then don’t need to go through that extra trouble of buying heels if you think it will make you look grander. Remember always wear something that you’re comfortable with. Wedding dresses are heavy and complex. In the midst of all that, you will need to walk around with high heels. You will feel awkward, look awkward and your legs will give up on you soon. Rather, we advise you to wear a mix of heels and flats so you can walk with the perfect grace.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5><strong>Pamper Your Feet</strong></h5>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-900\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/8035968c52a7051a2e0023cfde3d1270-1024x662.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"414\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-904\" src=\"https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/il_fullxfull.1263956752_t3bx-1024x684.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" />Wedding occasions take a long time to finish. Your feet are going to stay cramped inside your favorite shoes for 5-6 hours. This will deteriorate the condition of your feet and you will be more prone to aching and tiring legs. Have your feet pedicured before the ceremony, and exfoliate your feet every now and then. During the wedding day, Find excuses to get up from the stage and walk around for a bit to keep the blood flowing into your legs.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '5 things to keep in mind while buying wedding shoes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '537-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-09 10:32:13', '2019-01-09 10:32:13', '', 537, 'https://ayojok.com/ideas-and-stories/2019/01/09/537-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
